nodes.text: Battle of unidentified Outer Rim planet
A battle took place on a planet in the Outer Rim Territories in 21 BBY.

The separatist's fleet arrived in orbit of the planet and launched starfighters to attack the Venator-class Star Destroyer commanded by Admiral Wullf Yularen. The Republic forces defeated the fighters but later a Separatist frigate joined the battle and managed to damage the Star Destroyer. Despite this, the Confederacy of Independent Systems's fleet was destroyed.
